answers.body_markdown:
Looks like one cannot override the `index options` for a field after the field has  been initial  set in mapping

Example:

    put test
    put test/business/_mapping
    {
       
          &quot;properties&quot;: {
             &quot;name&quot;: {
                &quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot;,
               &quot;index_options&quot;: &quot;freqs&quot;,
                &quot;norms&quot;: {
                   &quot;enabled&quot;: false
                }
             }
          }
       
    }
    put test/business/_mapping
    {
       
          &quot;properties&quot;: {
             &quot;name&quot;: {
                &quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot;,
                &quot;index_options&quot;: &quot;docs&quot;,
                &quot;norms&quot;: {
                   &quot;enabled&quot;: false
                }
             }
          }
       
